IRS Announces Higher Personal Exemptions, Deductions for 2012

-- B y   S t e v e n   S l o a n
-- 
2011-10-20T14:20:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/irs-announces-higher-personal-exemptions-deductions-for-2012.html
The  Internal Revenue Service  will
increase for 2012 the value of personal exemptions and standard
deductions and widen tax brackets to account for inflation, the
agency said.  The change also affects tax credits and the per-person
exemption from the estate tax, the agency said in a release
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
